<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们坐在树下，又冷又饿，可是又无处可去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想回家。”简在发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果没人认识你是谁的话，变漂亮一点意思都没有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“天黑了。”鲍比指着天空说。“我们该怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42199</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们难过地看着太阳落下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等！”赛伊突然说，“你们感觉到了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都觉得自己的脸上笼上了一团薄雾，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像他们早上和休伊在一起时感觉到的那样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们小心地你看看我，我看看你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“潘瑟！是你！”赛伊开心地大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像休伊说的那样，太阳一落山一切都恢复到从前的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我能变回自己实在太高兴了！”潘瑟大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比也说：“我也是。现在我们回家吃饭吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们到家的时候，玛莎阿姨等在门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看到你们我实在是太高兴了。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她给了每个孩子一个大大的拥抱和亲吻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她告诉了他们有几个奇怪的孩子闯进家里的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我差点都要犯心脏病了。”她大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们怎么会知道我的名字，我一直想不明白。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个晚上的晚餐不同寻常地安静。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们都谨慎地不提起关于休伊或他们的愿望的任何事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139356</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147555</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他们单独在一起的时候，他们就立刻开始大谈特谈了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147556</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊举起了手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等一下！等一下！”他说，“潘瑟，你先说。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想说，我为今天的事情感到很抱歉。”她轻声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得我们不应该再去见休伊了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人表示反对。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不公平！”鲍比抱怨说，“我还没许愿呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，我也想许愿。”简嘀咕道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得至少我们每个人都许一次愿才公平。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>”赛伊对大家的说法表示同意，“那么明天，我先来许愿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂，为什么你第一个？”鲍比打断了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为我是年龄最大的。”赛伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“下一个就是鲍比，然后是简，好吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他孩子点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一大早，孩子们就出发去见休伊了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好！好！”休伊咧着嘴笑，“变得英俊美丽的感觉怎么样啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好，谢谢！”潘瑟迅速不诚实地回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们今天的愿望是什么？”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的鳍不停晃动着，他的脑袋也来回转动着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望......”赛伊激动地说，“我们都变得有钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多么有钱？”休伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊抓了抓脑袋。“嗯，这个……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊指向了木桶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“足够填满这个的钱？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊搓了搓手，说：“请给我们足够装满二十个这样的桶的钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们想要金子？银子？”休伊问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊又抓了抓脑袋。“金子。”他回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊舒展开了他的鳍，它们发出了金色的光芒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”鲍比屏着呼吸低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像魔法一样，二十个木桶出现了，然后天空中撒下了金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“下金子雨啦！”简尖叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们怎么搬得动啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊指着那些装满了闪闪发光的金币的桶问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊合上了他的鳍说：“那就是你们的事儿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331406</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他缩回了壳里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337977</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别忘了，日落的时候它们都会消失的。”他补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337978</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊将休伊送回了井底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342205</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们开始往自己的口袋里装金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>356445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能拿多少就拿多少！”赛伊努力劝说着大家，“越多越好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>